The correct query from getMappedObject should be:
{ "$and" : [ { "stat" : "A"} , { "disp" : { "$elemMatch" : { "$and" : [ { "res" : { "$ne" :  null }} , { "res" : { "$ne" : ""}}]}}}] , "batchId" : "5d0f1c53-92a2-48cb-8c84-1061769962c1"}
